  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/corefoundation\/cflocalekey\/usesmetricsystem\ncrawled: 2025-12-07T14:39:51Z\n---\n\n# usesMetricSystem\n\n**Type Property**\n\nSpecifies the whether the locale uses the metric system.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nstatic let usesMetricSystem: CFLocaleKey!\n```\n\n## Discussion\n\nThe corresponding value is a CFBoolean.\n\n## Constants\n\n- **identifier**: Specifies locale identifier.\n- **languageCode**: Specifies the locale language code.\n- **countryCode**: Specifies the locale country code.\n- **scriptCode**: Specifies the locale script code.\n- **variantCode**: Specifies the locale variant code.\n- **exemplarCharacterSet**: Specifies the locale character set.\n- **calendarIdentifier**: Specifies the locale calendar identifier.\n- **calendar**: Specifies the locale calendar.\n- **collationIdentifier**: Specifies the locale collation identifier.\n- **measurementSystem**: Specifies the measurement system used.\n- **decimalSeparator**: Specifies the decimal point string.\n- **groupingSeparator**: Specifies the separator string between groups of digits.\n- **currencySymbol**: Specifies the currency symbol.\n- **currencyCode**: Specifies the locale currency code.\n- **collatorIdentifier**: Specifies the collation identifier for the locale.\n\n",
